# Twisted Hearth Foundation - Project Overview

## Project Description
A Halloween-themed event management application built with React, TypeScript, Vite, and Supabase. Features include event RSVP, costume gallery, admin management, and interactive elements.

## Technology Stack
- **Frontend**: React 18 + TypeScript + Vite
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui components
- **Backend**: Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth + Storage)
- **Deployment**: Firebase Hosting
- **AI Integration**: Lovable AI platform

## Key Features
- Event RSVP system with email confirmations
- Costume gallery with image carousel
- Admin panel for event management
- User authentication and profiles
- Mobile-responsive design
- Interactive fog background effects

## Development Environment
- Node.js with npm/yarn
- Git for version control
- Firebase CLI for deployment
- Supabase CLI for database management

